You can provide replacement item for compoment not supported by old clients with <b>alt</b> property. 

This replacement component could be replaced for event older client apps. Length of replacement chain is not limited.

Read more: <a href="https://welltory.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/DEV/pages/129303740">Components</a>

Example:

{
    "title": "Components alternative",
    "content": [
        {
            "type": "ComponentIsNotSupportedAndHasNoReplacements"
        },
        {
            "type": "ComponentIsNotSupported",
            "alt": {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "This component is not supported but we have something to replace it"
            }
        }
    ]
}

